subSubSection.paragraph:
TERMINALIA. Body of penis elongate (W:L ratio: 0.26), 2 × as long as apodemes, widest at base, narrowing from base to basal ⅓ of length, from there widening apicad, constricted before apex, apex flat; in lateral view curvature stronger in basal ⅓, narrowing apicad in apical 1/4 (
Fig. 6A
).
